* REVERB
** a redo of -Jagarôth- verbs
** a redo of Jagaroth verbs

** kaf :: vi root :: go
** tikt :: vt root :: touch

** kafal- :: finite v :: goes
** tiktal- :: finite v :: touches

  # for the purposes of this document the spelling is simplified
* PRONOUNS and GENDER :: pronominal verbal endings
a   |--------------+--------+--------|
a   | 1s           | mem    | -en    |
a   | 1p           | memen  | -enen  |
a   | 2s           | teps   | -eps   |
a   | 2p           | tepsen | -epsen |
a   | 3s sapient   | teth   | -eth   |
a   | 3p insapient | tethen | -ethen |
a   | 3s sapient   | sos    | -os    |
a   | 3p insapient | sosen  | -osen  |
a   |--------------+--------+--------|

* the parameters: 
** -TENSE- there is no tense at all
** NUMBER :: singular, plural
** PERSON :: first, second, third
** GENDER :: Sapient, insapient
** VOICE :: active, passive
** FRAME :: infinitive, finite, participle
** ASPECT :: perfect, imperfect, inchoative, cessative


* NUMBER :: singular, plural
** tiktaleth tan sevinem ::
** The man touches my face.
** tiktalethen tanen sevinemen ::
** The men touch our faces.

