** nod :: nominal :: tomorrow
** wod :: nominal :: yesterday
** hod :: nominal :: today

* this is old :: there is no tense!!!!
** -TENSE- :: past, nonpast
*** He goes/is going to town.
*** /kafal tet borgot/ :: nonpast tense
*** go-FIN 3ss town-LOC
*** He went/was going to town.
*** /kafaltat tet borgot/ :: past tense
*** go-FIN-PAST 3ss city-LOC

